I don't express my feelings very well.
I'm crazy.

45
00:02:52,160 --> 00:02:52,600
But...

46
00:02:53,600 --> 00:02:55,640
...I hate him because...

47
00:02:58,240 --> 00:03:01,920
...I know the situation we're in but for one day...

48
00:03:02,480 --> 00:03:04,600
...just one day that he rests and says...

49
00:03:04,760 --> 00:03:09,240
..."for the rest of the year, I'm your father.
But today I'm your brother."

50
00:03:09,880 --> 00:03:11,520
But he doesn't.

